ðŸŒ• Moon Phase Simulator (/moon)
A fully functional interactive physics-based simulation.

Dual Views:
God Mode (Top-down): Shows the orbital mechanics of the Earth and Moon around the Sun.
Earth Mode (Observer): Shows the moon phase as seen from Earth.
Interactive Controls:
Timeline slider to scrub through the year.
Play/Pause and speed controls (Slow/Medium/Fast).
Educational Content:
Real-time calculation of moon phases (New Moon, Waxing Crescent, Full Moon, etc.).
Dynamic "Smart Tips" that explain phenomena like why the moon glows or tidal locking.
Visual correction to ensure the lit side of the moon always faces the sun.
